0Z","msg":"眾所周知淋病係想將個波比番我地，再放大暴力事件。<br />\n簡單d來講，我地文宣一直講警暴，一直講五大訴求，差d乜？ 就係無將個波比番佢呀！與其成日係度話咩唔做得唔做得，不如積極 d 將所有野推番比政府？ 聽日我要見到：<br />\n<br />\n。連農牆大大隻字寫住，政府管治不力，扮對話，無真正聽市民同市威者訴求，搞到而家咁！<br />\n。等車等巴士要大大聲講，政府乜都唔做、正係識龜縮，唔肯正視問題！<br />\n。同身邊既人，無論黃藍又好，大大力屌政府無能！<br />\n<br />\n獅鳥好暴力？裝飾好暴力？咪玩啦，你唔成日提，屌番政府咪無人覺得重要囉！"},{"pid":"b00dccaf5e862479bb241989b935acce0540e045","tid":1630510,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:14.000Z","msg":"五毛popo負皮還負皮<br />\n請面對現實"},{"pid":"29f0ac92dbcd9fb683d48955f653a7f554d084bb","tid":1630510,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"<strong></strong>"},{"pid":"252c99901683a88c63a46dc6ba2793c256b6edd5","tid":1630510,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:57:34.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"11041f68dd6d6472fc7fa3b05fa8ef15333a5b80","tid":1630510,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"<em></em>"},{"pid":"842b4f230418bfe8ec85f048e476b2aa24ed6e66","tid":1630510,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"They dont care.  所以政府呢班恐怖分子係冇底線。"},{"pid":"0b9eedd71f6c3c9b6d985ff655856de2201ba9ed","tid":1630510,"uid":201464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"842b4f230418bfe8ec85f048e476b2aa24ed6e66","tid":1630510,"uid":77547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:01:51.000Z","msg":"They dont care.  所以政府呢班恐怖分子係冇底線。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:06:25.000Z","msg":"及早俾大眾同外國認清呢個香港政府嘅真面目未嘗唔係一件壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4218470885242cd68ccb685f47daffcb6673d3c","tid":1630510,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:09:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟！一齊拆！</span></span><br />\n因為個宣言第一段有中共味道呀<br />\n中777同習圈套呀<br />\n<br />\n幫手report<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tfwXea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tfwXea.png&h=49b8c28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ParliamentHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FParliamentHK&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=460e5fe1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ParliamentHK</a><br />\n<br />\n對家已起底，見一個report 一個<br />\n見圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcqdrbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmcqdrbw.jpg&h=a4feb115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：共產黨玩嘢，香港人領嘢。咁都領嘢？枉為香港人。香港人不聽陳雲的話，犯上政治錯誤，犧牲幾多人都是被共產黨收割，之後糟蹋。<br />\n如果你識字，就知道第一句是共產黨的意識形態。破舊立新，而且強調歷史發展的必然性。<br />\n香港人昨晚十八區，宣讀共產主義宣言，而且宣言隻字不提美國為香港人權立法監護香港的貢獻，美國的有識之士被香港人激死了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157462752772225?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157462752772225%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=780176e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157462752772225?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時有香港獨立黨出聲明攻擊香港人權及民主法、又有臨時議會成立、又有臨時政府成立、又有連登「我有個讀政治的朋友」寫了香港憲法？同時又有練乙燈出文再提港獨？全部舉動幾日內急急推出，全部都是指向推翻美國「人權及民主法」的保障香港自治的立法前設？全部都是港共用了緊急法之後才忽然出現？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100002094159071/posts/2498430470236734?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100002094159071%2Fposts%2F2498430470236734%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6vFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=9700dec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100002094159071/posts/2498430470236734?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"ecca978467bce2f25aaa4c3472685cc588a20da0","tid":1630510,"uid":202577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:10:13.000Z","msg":"因為中共最根本考慮唔是呢d野<br />\n是保住自己政權/特權/個人利益<br />\n尤其是而家個位大帝"},{"pid":"6a593911538639c6f0a32dab20eea01d7e59d953","tid":1630510,"uid":94982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:11:55.000Z","msg":"佢理撚得你,最緊要政權穩定"},{"pid":"d6dfeddbcc28f3569563b2407dac08ee0a589b80","tid":1630510,"uid":166236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"中共六四屠城都做得出"},{"pid":"824e58e055a7ee72a922abbaa370ee00292cd610","tid":1630510,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:07.000Z","msg":"贏咗場運動<br />\n輸咗個香港<br />\n值得咩？"},{"pid":"ada4bebe7986e8f46324606b40bb3caec49523df","tid":1630510,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:16:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr